  </section>  <section>
    <h2>3. Project Objectives</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Analyze state-wise and year-wise property theft and recovery data.</li>
      <li>Identify recovery performance patterns and disparities.</li>
      <li>Provide actionable insights and data-backed recommendations.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>  <section>
